{"tid":1484744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲留喺金鐘嘅勇武，你唔值得我尊重！","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:19:30.000Z","uid":198088,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"acbe6c8136c920fda06ff47af4d18de87e568226","tid":1484744,"uid":198088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:04:29.000Z","msg":"成日都話要尊重前線，要相信前線決定，咁你呢？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你有冇尊重過今日嘅主辦方民陣？有冇尊重過其他出來嘅市民</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n今日嘅主題係乜嘢？你哋唔記得啦？留喺金鐘目的係乜嘢？有咩好處？你答到我嘅你就繼續留飽佢！<br />\n<br />\n今日主題係乜嘢，唔該你自己諗下？係咪要各自為戰？係咪要衰收尾？係咪要送頭？屋企需要你啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果你唔係鬼，又唔肯走，唔係我同你割蓆，係你同我哋割蓆！</span></span>"},{"pid":"80752a39e52c0ae98b9ba2e03a1d18d0425635d9","tid":1484744,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:06:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3663c80c81da12612b3b3ef32c08ff80d5d2fc0d","tid":1484744,"uid":147345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:07:34.000Z","msg":"唔好分勇武同和理非，在場大部分都係冇gear"},{"pid":"4d37a9bf4cbb33730cc2c00980af6e52612f411b","tid":1484744,"uid":157666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"唔好話送唔送頭 <br />\n今日大家咁辛苦出黎行 <br />\n大家都等緊成績表<br />\n想睇下政府可以點回應<br />\n你有咩意外我唔理 亦都理唔到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但你會騎劫左聽日嘅全世界嘅報章頭版</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722513fb9313c10e8bb692ea867c5fce2223e11b","tid":1484744,"uid":157666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:10:30.000Z","msg":"仲留守嘅唔係勇武<br />\n係無腦!!"},{"pid":"5f23fa3cc27d6befeb92626b17eb62ef15f835dc","tid":1484744,"uid":198088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"快啲走！！！！！醒少少"}]}